{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Banger_vs_Chance",
  "title": "Banger vs. Chance",
  "summary": "In the third round of the 35 ISY fighter-simulator championship, Marshal Krieg Inrokana (Banger) duels his own former trainee, Squadron Leader Alex Dante, flying as Chance. Knowing Dante is no pilot to be lured into a trap, Krieg opens with disciplined aggression while Dante stays calm, keeping her fighter light and maneuverable. The two evenly matched aviators trade fire across several exchanges, each anticipating the other's habits from their shared training. Krieg's experience gradually tells, and he wears down Chance's craft to take the match. The duel underscores the respect between teacher and student even as Banger advances.",
